Raymond Cannon (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Raymond_Cannon_(actor) 0 Raymond Cannon (September 1, 1892 – June 7, 1977) was an American actor, film director, screenwriter, journalist, and author known for his work with D. W. Griffith and Buster Keaton.
